aling. Also, known variants of stochastic gradient descent\n(SGD) methods are shown to work.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Sat, 23 Jun 2018 21:15:26 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Fri, 22 Feb 2019 13:21:40 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Sun, 24 Nov 2019 20:06:19 GMT"}],"update_date":"2019-11-26"}
