 we can effectively identity top stories and quantify news\nsimilarity.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Sun, 24 Jun 2018 04:44:36 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Mon, 2 Jul 2018 00:01:57 GMT"}],"update_date":"2018-07-03"}
