ieve considerable transmission energy saving compared with both pure NOMA\nand TDMA schemes.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Sun, 24 Jun 2018 13:40:16 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Wed, 18 Dec 2019 12:39:41 GMT"}],"update_date":"2019-12-19"}
